name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: dfs.namenode.resource.du.reserved
description:
The amount of space to reserve/require for a NameNode storage directory
    in bytes. The default is 100MB. Support multiple size unit
    suffix(case insensitive), as described in dfs.blocksize.

name: dfs.namenode.available-space-rack-fault-tolerant-block-placement-policy.balanced-space-tolerance
description:
Only used when the dfs.block.replicator.classname is set to
    org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.blockmanagement.AvailableSpaceRackFaultTolerantBlockPlacementPolicy.
    Special value between 0 and 20, inclusive. if the value is set beyond the scope,
    this value will be set as 5 by default, Increases tolerance of
    placing blocks on Datanodes with similar disk space used.

name: dfs.qjournal.finalize-segment.timeout.ms
description:
Quorum timeout in milliseconds during finalizing for a specific
    segment.

name: hadoop.security.kms.client.encrypted.key.cache.num.refill.threads
description:
Number of threads to use for refilling depleted EncryptedKeyVersion
    cache Queues

name: net.topology.script.number.args
description:
The max number of args that the script configured with
    net.topology.script.file.name should be run with. Each arg is an
    IP address.

name: mapreduce.jobhistory.intermediate-user-done-dir.permissions
description:
The permissions of the user directories in
  ${mapreduce.jobhistory.intermediate-done-dir}. The user and the group
  permission must be 7, this is enforced.
